thread.title: Tracy Whitten

author: Tracy Whitten
title: Tracy Whitten
text:
I like TopCash. I do have a couple of displeasures, you might say. 1. When I invited other members to get the $10, they never could set up an account because it said they were already a member. It was my name they were seeing. 2. I'm a little confused as to why when I finally met my $20 mark for my American Express payout, I could only get $18+.
I will still keep using TopCash from time to time, but I would like to have given it 5 stars.
